        {
            "title": "大公司创新情报（5月9日）：首批科创债发行名单披露 2家深圳企业现身",
            "description": "<article class=\"post-body\" data-v-1d7d601f=\"\">\n<h3 style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">今日看点</span>\n</h3>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/9ef6a4d74465812c55c487123c42adb0?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\"><strong style=\"font-size: 18px;\">首批科创债发行名单披露 2家深圳企业现身</strong></a><br/>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;display: block;\">\n</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/54645273e9dd9e77ecf8a02f942c995e?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\"><strong style=\"font-size: 18px;\"> 云锋金融(00376)盘中涨超20% 近七日累涨1.5倍 蚂蚁集团内部有望实现业务协同</strong></a><br/>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;display: block;\">\n</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/5bdf98cf563dbefdca019669da2c1377?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\"><strong style=\"font-size: 18px;\">比亚迪海狮07DM-i正式上市</strong></a><br/>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;display: block;\">\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:11pt\">\n<br/>\n</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n        今日情报（15家16条）\n    </h3>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/bc160d9ff902a4f8679978d32c744931/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">立讯精密</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/9ef6a4d74465812c55c487123c42adb0?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">首批科创债发行名单披露 2家深圳企业现身</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/488c459718bb9a750996affabf599189/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">蚂蚁集团</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/54645273e9dd9e77ecf8a02f942c995e?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\"> 云锋金融(00376)盘中涨超20% 近七日累涨1.5倍 蚂蚁集团内部有望实现业务协同</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/d7ed6785447a172e229f2ee8abfadf4f/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">比亚迪</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/5bdf98cf563dbefdca019669da2c1377?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">比亚迪海狮07DM-i正式上市</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/440290645201243c163947651758abd5/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">中国移动</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/d3986d222e8e6898112abbe783ab31dc?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">香港宽频(01310)股东将股票由法国巴黎银行转入中国国际金融香港证券 转仓市值7.58亿港元</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/dd88e183fc79ab787be7e1cd4cb3da47/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">宁德时代</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/bdb0a2a9050446c620f211020ac0f25f?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">宁德时代发布全球首款9MWh储能系统</a><br/><a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/f904c4686e6aa068f8daddf7d320341c?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">财联社5月8日电，据报道，宁德时代正在考虑，在下周一启动香港上市簿记建档时，仅设定一个最高价格。</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/12206edd7570cc5ee81346b046c8467f/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">小米集团</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/a8add41c2bdef79b3cdb9bb28b575dae?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">小米空调系长虹生产？小米怎么说</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/733fdf5cb2f803f31afda052434133eb/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">恒瑞医药</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/b956bb234331096773fa2d76c57a1892?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">恒瑞医药：药品上市许可申请获受理</a>\n</p>\n<ul class=\"list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: disc;\">\n<li>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/company/details/2d55259fcb4200d6a3485b9b0cfffc6b/profile?source=iyiou.dgs\" target=\"_blank\">理想汽车</a>\n</strong></span>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: left;\">\n<a href=\"https://data.iyiou.com/intelligence/details/472f6500baf